{"id": 232039050, "title": "Meet Ram Mohan Naidu, 3-time Andhra MP and India&#039;s youngest-ever Union minister", "text": "Telugu Desam Party (TDP) MP from Andhra Pradesh's Srikakalum, Kinjarapu Ram Mohan Naidu, was sworn-in as part of the Modi 3.0 government on Sunday. The 36-year-old MP is one of the youngest ministers of the Prime Minister Modi-led Cabinet. Son of former union minister and TDP leader K Yerran Naidu, Ram Mohan left his work in Singapore and joined politics after his father's death in a road accident in 2012.Ram Mohan contested and won the 2014 Lok Sabha elections from Srikakulam at the age of 26 and became the second-youngest MP to be elected that year.Who gets which ministry in Modi 3.0? Form your 'Dream Cabinet' and win prizes.link__elec{padding:0 0 12px} .link__elec div{margin-bottom:7px;}.link__elec a{color: var(--linkcolor); text-decoration: underline;font-size:18px; line-height:24px; font-weight:600;} He worked as the TDP national general secretary, even during critical times such as when TDP chief Chandrababu Naidu was arrested in the skill development scam.The TDP leader was one of the first MPs to advocate for menstrual health education and sex education in Parliament. He has also campaigned for the removal of GST on sanitary pads.Ram Mohan is the national general secretary of the TDP.Ram Mohan won the 2024 Lok Sabha polls from Srikakulam with a margin of over 3.27 lakh votes.Narendra Modi took oath for a third consecutive term as Prime Minister, along with 72 ministers, at the Rashtrapati Bhavan.Published By: Ashutosh AcharyaPublished On: Jun 9, 2024Must Watch", "summary": "<a href=\"https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/ram-mohan-naidu-modi-cabinet-ministry-tdp-lok-sabha-srikakulam-2551058-2024-06-09\"> <img align=\"left\" hspace=\"2\" height=\"180\" width=\"305\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/ram-mohan-naidu-090851373-16x9_0.png?VersionId=XJ.BKGC95cn1iQn1R9XYRQTMuqLhN3xi\"> </a> Meet Ram Mohan Naidu, 3-time Andhra MP and India's youngest-ever Union minister", "url": "https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/ram-mohan-naidu-modi-cabinet-ministry-tdp-lok-sabha-srikakulam-2551058-2024-06-09", "image": "https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/ram-mohan-naidu-090851373-16x9_0.png?VersionId=XJ.BKGC95cn1iQn1R9XYRQTMuqLhN3xi?size=1280:720", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-09 15:24:07", "author": null, "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "in", "sentiment": 0.23}